COMPANY RATINGS
PlanetFeedback.com compiles ratings on companies based on the opinions and satisfaction levels of consumers. To see how your company stacks up, or to see how your competitors are doing, please click on http://www.planetfeedback.com/ratings. To find out how PlanetFeedback.com creates and updates the company ratings, click on http://www.planetfeedback.com/ratings/learnmore.

WHAT WE OFFER
As a service to businesses, PlanetFeedback offers ExpressFeedback, a faster and more efficient way to handle Web-based consumer feedback. The benefit to companies? Increased revenue, lower costs associated with handling real-time feedback, enhanced consumer insight, and satisfied, more loyal customers. ExpressFeedback can be up and running
in a matter of weeks. For more information and a emonstration of ExpressFeedback, please visit PlanetFeedback's business Web site at http://biz.planetfeedback.com/biz, e-mail us at B2B@planetfeedback.com or call sales at (513) 618-6700.

IS THIS LETTER FINDING ITS WAY TO YOU CORRECTLY?
We want to be sure that this consumer letter finds it way to you smoothly. All PlanetFeedback letters are addressed to your company's CEO, but if someone else on your staff is better equipped to handle customer feedback, please send the correct contact information for that e-mail account and we'll direct the letter accordingly. E-mail the correct information to companyinfo@email.planetfeedback.com, fax it to (513) 618-6702 or mail it to PlanetFeedback, 1128 Main St., Cincinnati, OH 45210-5300. Please include the name of your company. Thanks!

